♪Drifting aimlessly♪

2
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Not knowing where to go♪

3
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:36,540
♪The moonlight tonight feels sorrowful♪

4
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:42,260
♪I stand alone against it♪

5
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,620
♪But I don't want to♪

6
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:50,780
♪The longing catches me off guard♪

7
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:58,380
♪To the silent night, I surrender myself♪

8
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,500
♪Tossing and turning, lost in confusion♪

9
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:10,620
♪In the darkness, I lose my way♪

10
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:32,940
[Bound by Sin]

11
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:35,980
[Episode 13]

12
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,560
From what position are you having

13
00:01:38,790 --> 00:01:39,920
this meeting with us today?

14
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,680
Naturally, I'm speaking as the head of the Jiang family.

15
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:47,680
The invitations I sent to all of you today

16
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,150
were stamped with the seal of the head of the family, right?

17
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,400
What?

18
00:01:52,230 --> 00:01:54,870
Did Jiang Zhen really hand control

19
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,120
over to you?

20
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:58,510
I bet you took advantage of your father being sick

21
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,200
and secretly seized the seal.

22
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:04,710
You think you can fool us with such underhanded tricks?

23
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,710
If you don't believe me,

24
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,400
you can go to the hospital yourselves.

25
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,080
My father woke up this afternoon.

26
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:19,280
[Jiang's Trading Company]
You can take a look at these documents.

27
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,180
[Jiang's Trading Company]

28
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:34,630
Jiang Yingxian,

29
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:36,470
what's your game here?

30
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,280
Are you trying to threaten us with these?

31
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:41,710
Third uncle,

32
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,910
please calm down.

33
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,190
If I know about this,

34
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,870
my father certainly does too.

35
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,680
Since he hasn't questioned

36
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,870
your accounts,

37
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,960
I won't either.

38
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,630
Yingxian,

39
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,710
I don't have a problem

40
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:03,280
with you taking charge from here on out.

41
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,910
But, you see,

42
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,400
the way you're going about this

43
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,470
is putting everyone in a difficult position.

44
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,630
Uncles,

45
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,520
do you know what's happening to the Lu family?

46
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,430
The Lu family?

47
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:21,520
I heard Governor Jin raided their house.

48
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,150
What does that have to do with us?

49
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,590
There's war everywhere now.

50
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,680
The Revolutionary Army is already here.

51
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:33,030
I'm sure you've all heard

52
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,030
many different versions

53
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:36,280
of the story.

54
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,680
But at the end of the day,

55
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:41,800
the Nan Army is running out of money.

56
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,120
Right now,

57
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:49,120
only I can help the Jiang family get through this.

58
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,910
You?

59
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,000
With your fiancé?

60
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,190
You think he can save our family?

61
00:03:57,470 --> 00:03:58,120
Well,

62
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,310
I have my ways.

63
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,000
Yingxian,

64
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,680
if you really can save the Jiang family,

65
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,150
I'll accept you as head of the family.

66
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,430
Now, Shen Dongyang

67
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,190
is the last one to deal with.

68
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:50,830
Yingxian,

69
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:53,270
this is the first time you've let me stay the night.

70
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:55,390
I'm so happy.

71
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,560
Dongyang,

72
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,680
do you really want to marry me?

73
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:24,060
♪In my eyes, it's starting to rain again♪

74
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:27,580
♪I turn around and bury the past♪

75
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:30,220
♪In a daze, I see you♪

76
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:35,140
♪How sweet we once were♪

77
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:38,860
♪Now I'm left standing here alone♪

78
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:42,500
♪The words left unsaid still linger in my heart♪

79
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:46,860
♪The cat we raised is still at home♪

80
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:50,220
♪Is it waiting for you...♪

81
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,190
I've seen you many times before.

82
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,920
Your father keeps bringing you to all these banquets.

83
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:03,190
He never stops bragging about you.

84
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,750
Really?

85
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,000
So that's what everyone thinks.

86
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:09,270
I'm flattered.

87
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:14,740
♪When the meteors streak across the sky♪

88
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,620
♪And sink into the deep sea...♪

89
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,430
Want one?

90
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,510
No, thanks.

91
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,980
♪Hiding away the roaring waves...♪

92
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:27,310
Your eyes say otherwise.

93
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:30,070
Doesn't it get tiring, always acting so composed?

94
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,680
Isn't life about struggling?

95
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,390
Besides,

96
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:38,750
smoking cigarettes is no fun.

97
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,920
If you're going to smoke, go for a cigar.

98
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,680
For Shen Dongyang,

99
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:55,480
that little spark of attraction

100
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:59,190
wasn't enough to make him give up power and wealth.

101
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,040
Yingxian,

102
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:09,240
you're not still upset about what happened

103
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,800
in Haicheng, are you?

104
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,310
It was just a random question.

105
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,430
Maybe I'm having pre-wedding anxiety.

106
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,040
I've been overthinking a lot.

107
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:24,000
I do think you've been overthinking a lot lately.

108
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,680
If I don't marry you,

109
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,560
who should I marry instead?

110
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,830
Well,

111
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,600
your true love.

112
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,360
My true love?

113
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,120
Who's that?

114
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:41,630
That's something only you know.

115
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:44,270
What if

116
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,270
it's you?

117
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,240
Are you upset that I sent you to Haicheng,

118
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,630
or did you meet someone new

119
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,510
while you were there?

120
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,000
Don't tell me

121
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,950
it's that bodyguard with a pretty face.

122
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,310
Shen Dongyang,

123
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,240
are you jealous?

124
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,920
And if I am?

125
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,310
You know

126
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:28,800
how possessive I am of you.

127
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,870
That's not like you at all.

128
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,080
Besides,

129
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,840
I don't think you have the right to be jealous.

130
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:40,120
Don't look at me like that, Dongyang.

131
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,360
I've never interfered

132
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,630
with what you do outside.

133
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,000
Jiang Yingxian,

134
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:49,630
the political and business worlds in the Nanli District

135
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,390
are on the brink of collapse.

136
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,630
I just hope our families

137
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,630
can work together to get through this disaster,

138
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,840
instead of ending up in a lose-lose situation.

139
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,440
To that end, you and I

140
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:04,630
are in this together.

141
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:08,150
So, Dongyang, you still care about my family, huh?

142
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,150
I thought

143
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,670
you were putting me and my family

144
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:14,150
at risk so you could be with Zhou Xiaoqing.

145
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,440
So, you're upset because of her?

146
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,240
She's been with you for so long.

147
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,510
Haven't you thought about being with her for real?

148
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,120
How can she ever

149
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,270
compare to you?

150
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,030
I'm tired.

151
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:43,750
I won't see you out.

152
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,030
Jiang Yingxian,

153
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:53,510
you're really testing the limits of my gentlemanly patience.

154
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,790
I thought it'd be easier to break off the engagement

155
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,600
by teaming up with Zhou Xiaoqing.

156
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:12,240
I wonder what Fu Cheng is doing now.

157
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,600
Major Cheng,

158
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,870
there's a letter for you.

159
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,340
[To Fu Cheng]

160
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,550
Is it from your girlfriend?

161
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,440
What's wrong?

162
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,080
Did something happen back home?

163
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:45,150
It's nothing.

164
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:46,790
You go ahead.

165
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:49,600
I'll head back for a bit.

166
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,360
Jiang Yingxian!

167
00:11:57,460 --> 00:12:00,020
♪When can I♪

168
00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:03,140
♪Stop panicking?♪

169
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:10,580
♪I seem to accept the hard living calmly♪

170
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:15,860
♪Ran, walked, and spun like a top♪

171
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:18,580
♪Keep striving♪

172
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:24,740
