173
00:12:26,780 --> 00:12:30,780
♪When I take off the evening dress naked♪

174
00:12:31,060 --> 00:12:34,660
♪But my eyes still look dull♪

175
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:39,010
♪The air is filled with helplessness and despair♪

176
00:12:39,220 --> 00:12:41,820
♪Sadness has nowhere to hide♪

177
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:46,380
♪I might as well cry and let go of the past♪

